man slipped away unobserved, and I saw no more of him till he became my comrade 
on the sea. In a few minutes, however, he was missed by his shipmates, and 
being, it seems, for some reason a huge favourite with them, they raised a cry 
of “Bulkington! Bulkington! where’s Bulkington?” and darted out of the 
house in pursuit of him.
